NK037(ji)002:1: // dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs las bzhi'i snye ma zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)002:2: dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs las bzhi'i snye ma zhes bya ba /
NK037(ji)002:4: he ru ka dpal thugs rjes khros pa'i sku //
NK037(ji)002:5: ma rungs bdud dpung mthar mdzad nag po che //
NK037(ji)002:6: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag por gus btud nas //
NK037(ji)002:7: de yi sgrub thabs don bsdus mdo tsam bri //
NK037(ji)002:8: 'di nyid kyi dbang thob cing dam tshig la gnas
NK037(ji)002:9: pa'i sngags pas nyer dgu la sogs pa'i dus khyad
NK037(ji)002:10: par can la / bris sku mchod gtor nye bar
NK037(ji)002:11: mkho ba'i yo byad thams cad mthong brgyud bzhin tshogs
NK037(ji)002:12: par can la / par byas nas / bdag bskyed kyi rnal 'byor sngon du 'gro bas /
NK037(ji)002:13: mchod pa spyi dang sman gtor rak+ta rnams byin gyis brlab /
NK037(ji)002:14: mdun bskyed kyi rten bsang sbyang /
NK037(ji)002:15: stong pa'i ngang las mdun gyi nam mkhar khrag zhag
NK037(ji)002:16: 'khrug pa'i klong ma la ya gnam lcags 'bar ba'i
NK037(ji)002:17: do / rab tu 'jigs shing skyi g.ya' ba'i gnas su /
NK037(ji)002:18: dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal yas khang chen po'i lte
NK037(ji)002:19: bar pad+ma dang nyi ma'i steng du mi ro dang
NK037(ji)002:20: rta ro la gnas pa'i h'u las gri gug h'u
NK037(ji)002:21: gis mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las dpal ye
NK037(ji)002:22: shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po chen po
NK037(ji)002:23: rdo rje srin po'i gzugs can sku mdog mthing nag
NK037(ji)002:24: thung zhing sbom la yan lag rags pa nyi ma
NK037(ji)002:25: 'bum gyi gzi brjid can zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan
NK037(ji)002:26: gsum pa / zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa'i gra nas khrag 'dzag pa /
NK037(ji)002:27: ljags 'dril zhing drag po'i skan sgra rdeb pa /
NK037(ji)002:28: khro gnyer bsdus pa'i shangs nas 'thor byed kyi lung sgra 'byin pa /
NK037(ji)002:29: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum sdang mig tu ldog pa /
NK037(ji)002:30: dbu skra dang sma ra smin ma kham nag gyen
NK037(ji)002:31: du 'bar ba las skar chen gyi 'od 'phro ba
NK037(ji)002:32: / phyag g.yas 'bar ba'i gri gug dang g.yon gdug
NK037(ji)002:33: pa can gyi khrag gis gang ba'i thod pa thugs
NK037(ji)002:35: mchan g.yas su tsan dan gyi beng chen gzer ba'i
NK037(ji)002:36: beng stod nas lha dmag 'bum dang beng smad nas
NK037(ji)002:37: bdud dmag nyi khri chig stong 'gyed pa /
NK037(ji)002:38: sku la dar nag gi 'jol ber brtsegs mar gsol
NK037(ji)002:39: zhing gser sked nor bu'i mig tshangs can bcings pa
NK037(ji)002:40: / thod pa skam po rigs lnga'i rtse phran can gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK037(ji)002:41: rlon pa khrag 'dzag pa lnga bcu dang rdo rje'i do shal 'phyang ba /
NK037(ji)002:42: yan lag sbrul gyis dkris shing mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs sogs dur khrod 'jigs pa'i chas can /
NK037(ji)002:43: sag t+wi'i lhwam yu ring gsol nas g.yon brkyang pa'i
NK037(ji)002:44: stabs kyis 'gying zhing brjid pas dgra bgegs rnams bardzisa
NK037(ji)002:45: pa / gtum zhing mi bsrun pa'i nyams can /
NK037(ji)002:46: spyi bor bya khyung nag po 'phur zhing lding ba /
NK037(ji)002:47: sta zur gnyis na seng ge ral pa sprug pa /
NK037(ji)002:50: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na khams
NK037(ji)002:51: gsum dbang du sdud cing srid gsum zil gyis gnon
NK037(ji)002:52: pa'i bdag nyid can du bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)002:53: de'i g.yon du nyi ma dang ro'i gdan la yum
NK037(ji)002:54: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma sku mdog sngon mo zhal
NK037(ji)002:55: gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa ral pa mthur du
NK037(ji)002:56: gtibs pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba /
NK037(ji)002:57: zhing gi pags pas stod g.yogs shing nyi zla gza' skar dang 'ja' 'od 'khrugs pa /
NK037(ji)002:58: stag lpags dang re lde'i smad dkris can /
NK037(ji)002:59: sbrul nag gi 'phyang 'phrul dang chu srin gyi thod pas brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)002:60: g.yas sbrul zhags dang g.yon thod skyogs rus bcud rkang
NK037(ji)002:61: klad dang 'bru mar khrag chang gis gang ba rol
NK037(ji)002:62: zhing stob pa / g.yas su las kyi mgon po
NK037(ji)002:63: mdog nag cing mi sdug pa'i gzugs can skra kham
NK037(ji)002:64: pa gyen du bardzesa shing g.yas gri gug dang g.yon
NK037(ji)002:65: zhing stob pa / khrag thogs pa / g.yon brkyang
NK037(ji)002:66: gis ro'i gdan la bka' nod pa'i tshul gyis gnas
NK037(ji)002:67: zhing stob pa / khrag thogs pa / pa'o //
NK037(ji)002:68: de dag gi shar du h'u las khro chen badz+ra
NK037(ji)002:69: king ka ra sku mdog mthing nag rngams shing khros
NK037(ji)002:70: pa'i nyams can zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK037(ji)002:71: g.yas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bskor zhing dmigs pa'i mgo lus 'dral ba /
NK037(ji)002:72: g.yon thod pa dgra bo'i snying khrag gis gang ba zhal du gsol ba /
NK037(ji)002:73: mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs dang stag lpags kyi smad dkris can sbrul dang thod pas brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)002:74: gri thogs ging chen bcu gnyis sogs las byed dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)002:75: lhor ya las gnod sbyin zangs mdog dmar nag kha gdangs shing skan sgra rdeb pa /
NK037(ji)002:76: sdang mig gis dgra dpung sreg cing ral pa dmar po sprin ltar gtibs pa /
NK037(ji)002:77: g.yas gser gyi spu gri 'phyar zhing g.yon bse mdung 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)002:78: yum bse gdong zangs mgrin can dmar nag 'ja' tshon
NK037(ji)002:79: gyi gos can byad thag dang nad rkyal thogs pa
NK037(ji)002:82: mi dmar bshan pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sogs las byed dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)002:83: nub tu dza las gza' bdud chen po ra hu
NK037(ji)002:84: la sku mdog dud kha srin po'i gzugs can mgo
NK037(ji)002:85: bo dgu la lus kun mig gis gang zhing gtum
NK037(ji)002:86: rngams 'khrugs pa'i nyams can g.yas gri gug 'phyar ba'i
NK037(ji)002:87: rtse las skyin thang gi 'khor lo bskor zhing /
NK037(ji)002:88: g.yon thod khrag rngub cing chu srin gyi zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK037(ji)002:89: sku smad sbrul du 'khril zhing zhing gi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK037(ji)002:90: thod sbrul gyi phreng ba sogs 'jigs pa'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)002:93: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad sogs srid gsum dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK037(ji)002:94: byang du ma las 'dod khams bdag mo re ma
NK037(ji)002:95: t+ai nag mo skem zhing rid la gtum pa'i nyams
NK037(ji)002:96: can zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa'i bar du
NK037(ji)002:97: mi ro rengs po gsol ba /
NK037(ji)002:98: drag po'i skan sgra rdeb cing shangs nas nad kyi na bun 'thul ba /
NK037(ji)002:99: lte ba nas nyi ma 'char zhing spyi bor zla ba tshes pa /
NK037(ji)002:100: thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang thod rlon gyi do shal can /
NK037(ji)002:101: snyan g.yas seng ge dang g.yon pa sbrul dang dril bus brgyan pa /
NK037(ji)002:102: g.yas khram shing 'phyar zhing g.yon nad rkyal dgra la 'gyed pa /
NK037(ji)002:103: mi lpags gyi stod g.yogs dang re lde'i smad dkris
NK037(ji)002:104: sbrul gyi ske rags can drel rta rkang gsum srin
NK037(ji)002:105: po'i thod pa'i sga dang sbrul gyi gong smed can
NK037(ji)002:106: la chibs nas rak+ta'i rgya mtshor rol pa /
NK037(ji)002:107: nad kyi rkyal pa tshon gyi gru gu sho rdel
NK037(ji)002:108: dkar nag bdud kyi khram shing ste sprul pa'i mtshon
NK037(ji)002:109: cha lnga 'chang ba nag mo 'bum sde'i 'khor dang
NK037(ji)002:110: bcas te rlung nag 'tshubs ma'i dbus na bzhugs pa
NK037(ji)002:111: / de dag gi phyi rol du sprul pa dang
NK037(ji)002:112: yang sprul pho nya las byed sde brgyad dreg pa'i
NK037(ji)002:113: dmag tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pas bskor ba thams
NK037(ji)002:114: cad kyang phrin las 'dod rgur sgyur zhing sgrub pa
NK037(ji)002:115: po'i re ba skong bas nam mkha' bar snang sa
NK037(ji)002:116: gzhi thams cad yongs su gang bar gyur /
NK037(ji)002:117: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK037(ji)002:120: h'u las 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas /
NK037(ji)002:121: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas mchog 'og min
NK037(ji)002:122: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ma la ya gnam
NK037(ji)002:123: lcags 'bar ba'i ri bo dur khrod chen po brgyad
NK037(ji)002:124: sogs rang bzhin gyi gnas nas dpal mgon legs ldan
NK037(ji)002:125: tshogs kyi bdag po 'khor dang bcas pa mdun gyi
NK037(ji)002:126: nam mkhar sprin phung gtibs pa bzhin byon par bsam
NK037(ji)002:127: la lcags kyu'i rgya bcings te /
NK037(ji)002:128: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK037(ji)002:129: b+hurkura ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya hrim hrim ang+ku sha dza dzah zhes dang /
NK037(ji)002:131: lang+ka yul gyi grong brdal gyi //
NK037(ji)002:132: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK037(ji)002:133: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK037(ji)002:134: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK037(ji)002:135: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK037(ji)002:136: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas kyang //
NK037(ji)002:137: gsang sngags 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK037(ji)002:138: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa //
NK037(ji)002:139: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)002:140: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK037(ji)002:141: nye gnas kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma //
NK037(ji)002:142: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK037(ji)002:143: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs dang //
NK037(ji)002:144: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)002:146: pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK037(ji)002:147: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)002:149: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na
NK037(ji)002:150: pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra ma h+aa ka
NK037(ji)002:151: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK037(ji)002:152: / +aa kar+sha ya h'u dzah e a ra l+li hrim hrim dzahdzah zhes pa spyan drangs la /
NK037(ji)002:154: rdo rje brag chen gtams pa dang //
NK037(ji)002:155: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen khri //
NK037(ji)002:156: bam chen bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK037(ji)002:157: rab 'jigs dpa' bo 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NK037(ji)002:158: b+hurkura ma h+aa k+aa la rak+mo kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai
NK037(ji)002:159: nag mo ting lam sa ma ya s+t+wam ti sh+tha
NK037(ji)002:161: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK037(ji)002:162: badz+ra sa ma ya ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK037(ji)002:163: dpal rdo rje nag po chen po legs ldan tshogs
NK037(ji)002:164: kyi bdag po lcam dral 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK037(ji)002:165: kyis rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma
NK037(ji)002:166: dam pa rnams kyi bka' dang dam las ma 'da'
NK037(ji)002:167: bar sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs dam tshig
NK037(ji)002:168: gi gnyeng gtad / lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)002:169: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)002:170: dur khrod bdag po sgrol ba'i ging //
NK037(ji)002:172: a ti p+au hoh pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes pas phyag bya /
NK037(ji)002:174: stong gsum 'adi'am stong gsum gzhan dag na //
NK037(ji)002:175: me tog phreng ba la sogs rin chen dbyig /
NK037(ji)002:176: la du la phug la sogs yid bzhin zas //
NK037(ji)002:177: thang skyes chu skyes la sogs longs spyod rkyen //
NK037(ji)002:178: 'chi med bdud rtsi la sogs dam tshig chu //
NK037(ji)002:179: gu gul tshil chen la sogs bdug pa'i sprin //
NK037(ji)002:180: zhun chen mar me la sogs snang gsal mchog /
NK037(ji)002:181: bshos gtsang bza' btung longs spyod sna tshogs pa'i //
NK037(ji)002:182: rim gsum mchod pas tshogs bdag mnyes gyur cig /
NK037(ji)002:183: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ga na pa ti sa
NK037(ji)002:184: pa ri w+aa ra push+pe d+h+au pe +aa lo ke
NK037(ji)002:185: gan+d+he nee wi d+ya shap+da p+au dza hoh badz+ra r+au
NK037(ji)002:186: pa shap+da gan+d+he r+aa sa spar+she p+au dzahmh'u /
NK037(ji)002:187: zhes pa'i spyir mchod nas khyad par gyi mchod pa
NK037(ji)002:188: sman phud rak+ta gtor ma gsum 'bul tshig cho ga
NK037(ji)002:189: rigs mthun gzhan nas blangs pa'i mthar rtsa sngags la
NK037(ji)002:190: so so'i sngags btags nas phul /
NK037(ji)002:191: bye brag gtor ma la rak+ta bran nas dmigs bya dgug bstim bya /
NK037(ji)002:192: nang mchod bran la +aahmh'u gis sha khrag bdud rtsir spel la /
NK037(ji)002:194: rnal 'byor kun gyi dpal mgon mchog /
NK037(ji)002:195: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu rtsal can //
NK037(ji)002:196: dka' thub nag po tshur gson cig /
NK037(ji)002:197: legs ldan nag po ma rungs pa //
NK037(ji)002:198: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK037(ji)002:199: rang gi rgyal srid la gnas te //
NK037(ji)002:200: gzhan gyi sde rnam pham mdzad pa //
NK037(ji)002:201: khram la btab pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK037(ji)002:202: rol cig dgongs shig dam tshig gtso //
NK037(ji)002:203: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK037(ji)002:204: ces pa tsam gyi mthar gtso 'khor gyi sngags sham du /
NK037(ji)002:205: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)002:207: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)002:208: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)002:210: ma h+aa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)002:211: i dam d+h+au pe push+pe gan+d+he nee bi d+ya ba lim ta pi pa to hoh zhes mchod /
NK037(ji)002:214: lha min dmag tshogs g.yul bzlog cing //
NK037(ji)002:215: lha dmag dkar po'i dbugs 'byin pa'i //
NK037(ji)002:216: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)002:217: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK037(ji)002:218: bsod nams gzi brjid 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:219: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:220: spyod pa rlabs chen 'phags la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:221: drag shul mthu chen ldan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:222: pha rol phyin bcu mnga' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:223: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:224: bdag med gnyis rtogs khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:225: ston pa'i lung bstan thob la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:226: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams dang dgongs pa gcig /
NK037(ji)002:227: rig 'dzin grub thob rnams dang byin rlabs gcig /
NK037(ji)002:228: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams dang dam tshig gcig /
NK037(ji)002:229: lha srin sde brgyad rnams dang mthu rtsal gcig /
NK037(ji)002:230: sngon gyi drang srong rnams dang smon lam gcig /
NK037(ji)002:231: tshogs bdag khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:232: mgon po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)002:233: zhes pa tsam gyis bstod de zor yang ba'i dbang du byas la /
NK037(ji)002:234: shes na bstod pa rgyas pa gzhan du 'byung ba bzhin bya'o //
NK037(ji)002:235: de nas bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK037(ji)002:236: mgon po 'khor bcas kyi thugs kar nyi ma la
NK037(ji)002:237: gnas pa'i h'u yig la sogs pa'i mthar rang rang
NK037(ji)002:238: gi srog sngags rigs kyi kha dog can gyi bskor
NK037(ji)002:239: bar bdag bskyed kyi thugs ka'i sa bon las byung
NK037(ji)002:240: ba'i 'od zer gyis phog pas thugs kyi rgyud rab
NK037(ji)002:241: tu bskul bas ci 'dod pa'i phrin las rab 'byams
NK037(ji)002:242: thogs med du bsgrub par bsam la /
NK037(ji)002:243: b+hu ru ku ru i tsi ki byi u tsush+ma kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK037(ji)002:244: de lta ci 'grub bzlas pa'i mthar nyer spyod lnga dang nang mchod phul la /
NK037(ji)002:246: drag po sku lnga rgyal ba'i bka' sdod mchog /
NK037(ji)002:247: ye shes lnga ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i 'khor //
NK037(ji)002:248: phrin las bdud 'dul dgra bgegs kun gyi gshed //
NK037(ji)002:249: legs ldan 'khor dang bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)002:250: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsan cing dgos su gsol //
NK037(ji)002:251: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pas dgyes par mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:252: dam tshig 'ga' 'khrul nyams chag mthol zhing bshags //
NK037(ji)002:253: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)002:254: zhes bstod cing phrin las gsol /
NK037(ji)002:255: 'dir tshogs mchod byed na yi dam gang la brten pa de'i gzhung bzhin dang /
NK037(ji)002:256: yang na tshogs rdzas byin gyis brlab /
NK037(ji)002:257: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK037(ji)002:259: bar pa bskong bshags dang 'brel ba skong rdzas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK037(ji)002:261: bdag ni rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK037(ji)002:262: dam la gnas shing lha la 'phreng //
NK037(ji)002:263: khyod ni srung ma mthu rtsal can //
NK037(ji)002:264: sngon tshe dpal chen spyan snga ru //
NK037(ji)002:265: bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK037(ji)002:266: khyod kyi thugs dam gnyan po de //
NK037(ji)002:267: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bskul na //
NK037(ji)002:268: thugs dam dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)002:269: ma h+aa k+aa la gnas 'dir byon //
NK037(ji)002:270: legs ldan nag po dur khrod sgrol ging rdo rje
NK037(ji)002:271: sgrol byed sa bcu'i dbang phyug rig 'dzin srung ma
NK037(ji)002:272: rnal 'byor dgra lha tshogs bdag chen po gnas 'dir
NK037(ji)002:273: byon // bos so chos skyong snyan ma sra //
NK037(ji)002:274: g.yab bo legs ldan spyan ma rtul //
NK037(ji)002:275: sgrub bo tshogs bdag dgongs ma g.yel //
NK037(ji)002:276: bskul lo bdud rgyal mthu ma chung //
NK037(ji)002:277: do nub khyod kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)002:278: bskang ngo bskal pas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)002:280: me tog spos dang mar me dri //
NK037(ji)002:281: zhal zas rol mo'i bye brag dang //
NK037(ji)002:282: 'phan gdugs lhab lhub sna tshogs kyis //
NK037(ji)002:283: legs ldan 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)002:284: sha chen lnga ni ri ltar spungs //
NK037(ji)002:285: bdud rtsi lnga ni mtsho ltar bskyil //
NK037(ji)002:286: ye shes lnga ldan dam rdzas 'dis //
NK037(ji)002:287: dpal mgon 'khor bcas sha chen khrag dang dbang po lnga //
NK037(ji)002:288: tshil chen zhun mar mkhris pa dang //
NK037(ji)002:289: g.yang gzhi lhab lhub rkang gling sgras //
NK037(ji)002:290: dpal mgon 'khor bcas dmar chen bza' baca'i gtor ma dang //
NK037(ji)002:291: 'bru bcud bdud rtsi btung ba'i rgyun //
NK037(ji)002:292: khyad bar dam rdzas sna tshogs kyis //
NK037(ji)002:293: dpal mgon 'khor bcas gling bzhi gling phran ri rab dag /
NK037(ji)002:294: rin chen bdun dang bkra shis rdzas //
NK037(ji)002:295: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa yis //
NK037(ji)002:296: dpa' mgon 'khor bcas g.yag nag rta nag khyi nag dang //
NK037(ji)002:297: lug nag bya nag la sogs dang //
NK037(ji)002:298: rten pa'i dam rdzas sna tshogs kyis //
NK037(ji)002:299: dpal mgon 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK037(ji)002:301: bskang ngo bshags so thugs dam can //
NK037(ji)002:302: dam can thugs dam bskangs gyur nas //
NK037(ji)002:303: bdag gi nyams chag byang bar mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:304: dngos grub sgrub la bar gcod pa'i //
NK037(ji)002:305: 'gal rkyen bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK037(ji)002:306: mthun rkyen bsam pa thams cad sgrubs //
NK037(ji)002:307: rtag tu thugs dam ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)002:308: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:311: hoh yon tan lhun rdzogs dngos grub stsol mdzad pa'i //
NK037(ji)002:312: rtsa brgyud bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor lha //
NK037(ji)002:313: dpal chen rdo rje srin po khro bo'i rgyal //
NK037(ji)002:314: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)002:315: theg chen gsang sngags bla med sgor zhugs nas //
NK037(ji)002:316: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK037(ji)002:317: rtag tu bsrung zhing sdom par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:318: nyams chag 'gal 'khrul nongs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:319: thun bzhi'i rnal 'byor sgom par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:320: tha mal las la yengs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:321: bde gshegs thugs rgyud bskul bar khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:322: tha mal long gtam smras pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:323: dmigs med ye shes sgom par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:324: dug gsum rtog pa'i dbang gyur mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:325: phyi nang gsang rten 'dzugs par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:326: dgos pa'i dam rdzas ma tshang mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:327: rtag tu mchod bstod bsnyen par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:328: snyoms las le los g.yengs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:329: man ngag sbas nas sgrub par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:330: gsang ba'i gnyer kha 'chol ba mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:331: dam rdzas phud kyi mchod par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:332: 'bags btsog nyams par gyur pa rgyal ba'i bka' bzhin sgrub par khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:333: gzu lum ras chod bgyis pa zol med dam tshig bsrung bar khas blangs nas //
NK037(ji)002:334: nyams grib skyon gyis phog pa mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)002:335: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gi //
NK037(ji)002:336: dam tshig 'gal ba ma lus so sor bshags //
NK037(ji)002:337: mthol bshags 'bul lo tshangs par mdzad nas kyang //
NK037(ji)002:338: dngos grub mchog gis bdag rgyud gtams par mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:339: ces dang yig brgya mang du bazla'o //
NK037(ji)002:340: de ltar skong bshags skabs kyi phrin las la mkho ba'i dbang du byas kyi /
NK037(ji)002:341: rgyun gyi phrin las la ni /
NK037(ji)002:342: bzlas pa'i rjes kyi bstod pa phrin las gsol ba'i
NK037(ji)002:343: mthar thun gtor la dmigs bya bkug la bdud rtsir
NK037(ji)002:346: lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK037(ji)002:347: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK037(ji)002:348: nye gnas kro d+h+ai sha r+ai ma //
NK037(ji)002:349: ging dang gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK037(ji)002:350: ma mo mkha' 'gro pho nya dang //
NK037(ji)002:351: spul pa yang sprul 'khor dang bcas //
NK037(ji)002:352: zag med 'dod yon bdud rtsi yi //
NK037(ji)002:353: dam rdzas mchod gtor 'di bzhes la //
NK037(ji)002:354: deng 'dir bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:355: sngar bcol las kyi gtang rag mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:356: phyi bcol las kyi gsos su bzhes //
NK037(ji)002:357: sangs rgyas bstan pa khyod kyis srungs //
NK037(ji)002:358: dkon mchog dbu 'phangs khyod kyis bstod //
NK037(ji)002:359: slob dpon sku dgra khyod kyis thul //
NK037(ji)002:360: sgrub pa po yi stong grogs mdzod //
NK037(ji)002:361: ces gtor ma sgrub khang gi yang thog la sogs par 'bul lo //
NK037(ji)002:362: slar yang gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang nongs ba bshags /
NK037(ji)002:363: rten yod na brtan bzhugs dang /
NK037(ji)002:364: med na gtor mgron ye shes pa gshegs /
NK037(ji)002:365: dam tshig pa rang la bstim /
NK037(ji)002:366: gnas gsum du yi ge gsum gyi rgyas gdab /
NK037(ji)002:367: dge ba bsngo zhing shis pa brjod pas mtha' brgyan no //
NK037(ji)002:368: bstan srung rgya mtsho'i sde dpon nag po che //
NK037(ji)002:369: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i phrin las gzhung //
NK037(ji)002:370: snying por dril nas mdor bsdus 'dir brjod pa'i //
NK037(ji)002:371: bsod nams bstan pa rgyas pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK037(ji)002:372: dpal mgon legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i las byang
NK037(ji)002:373: rgyas pa las slar yang snying po khyer bder dril
NK037(ji)002:374: ba las bzhi'i snye ma zhes bya ba rig pa
NK037(ji)002:375: 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes bkod pa'i yi ge
